---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import MainCta from "../components/MainCta.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy | Metaphors Design";
const description = "Privacy Policy for Metaphors Design, an architectural practice based in Pune, India.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonicalURL="https://metaphors.design/privacy">
  <div class="bg-bone relative min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden">
    <Header />

    <main>
      <section class="relative w-full pt-48 pb-24 lg:pt-56 lg:pb-32">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 lg:px-12">
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
            <h1 class="text-charcoal mb-8 text-5xl leading-[1.05] font-light tracking-tight lg:text-7xl">
              Privacy Policy
            </h1>
            <p class="text-charcoal/60 mb-16 text-lg">
              Effective Date: January 1, 2026
            </p>

            <div class="prose prose-lg text-charcoal/80 prose-headings:text-charcoal prose-headings:font-light prose-h2:text-3xl prose-h2:mt-12 prose-h2:mb-6 prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-a:text-charcoal prose-a:underline hover:prose-a:text-charcoal/60 max-w-none">
              <p>
                At Metaphors Design, we are committed to protecting the privacy and security of our clients, partners, and website visitors. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or engage with our architectural services in Pune, India, and beyond.
              </p>

              <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
              <p>
                We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Contact us via email, phone, or through our website contact forms.</li>
                <li>Engage our architectural, interior design, or consultancy services.</li>
                <li>Subscribe to our newsletters or updates.</li>
              </ul>
              <p>
                This information may include your name, email address, phone number, physical address, and details related to your project inquiries.
              </p>

              <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
              <p>
                The information we collect is used in the following ways:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>To provide, operate, and maintain our services.</li>
                <li>To respond to your inquiries and offer customer support.</li>
                <li>To communicate with you regarding project updates, proposals, and relevant architectural insights.</li>
                <li>To improve our website and tailor our content to better serve our audience.</li>
              </ul>

              <h2>3. Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
              <p>
                As a professional architectural practice, client confidentiality is paramount. We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information only under the following circumstances:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> With trusted third-party contractors and consultants (e.g., structural engineers, landscape architects) who assist us in operating our business and delivering your project, provided they agree to keep this information confidential.</li>
                <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or in response to a valid legal request from authorities in India.</li>
              </ul>

              <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
              <p>
                We implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures designed to protect the security of any personal information we process. However, please be aware that no electronic transmission over the internet or information storage technology can be guaranteed to be 100% secure.
              </p>

              <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
              <p>
                Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights regarding your personal information, including the right to access, correct, or delete the personal data we hold about you. To exercise these rights, please contact us using the details provided below.
              </p>

              <h2>6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
              <p>
                We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. The updated version will be indicated by an updated "Effective Date" at the top of this policy.
              </p>

              <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
              <p>
                If you have questions or comments about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
              </p>
              <address class="not-italic mt-4">
                <strong>Metaphors Design</strong><br />
                Pune, Maharashtra, India<br />
                Phone: (+91) 96653 55522 / (+91) 98222 79173<br />
                Email: <a href="mailto:info@metaphors-design.com" class="text-charcoal underline">info@metaphors-design.com</a>
              </address>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <MainCta
      section={{
        eyebrow: "Engagement",
        headline: "Begin the Dialogue.",
        tagline: "You don't need a finished brief. Ambition and intent are enough to start the conversation.",
        ctaLabel: "Start the Conversation",
        ctaUrl: "/contact",
      }}
      className="bg-bone border-charcoal/10 border-t"
    />

    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
